    </ul>

    <ul class="portfolio-profile-p_list_unit">
      <h2 class="portfolio-profile-p_list_title">Education</h2>
      <ul class="portfolio-profile-p_education_unit">
        <li class="portfolio-profile-p_education_main_text">The University of Tokyo, Faculty of Law (Apr. 2018 - present)</li>
        <li class="portfolio-profile-p_education_sub_text">DepartmentⅠ: General Legal Studies Course</li>
      </ul>
      <ul class="portfolio-profile-p_education_unit">
        <li class="portfolio-profile-p_education_main_text">Taking a year off from university (Apr. 2017 - Mar. 2018)</li>
        <li class="portfolio-profile-p_education_sub_text">Lost the meaning of life</li>
